\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Katie and Sarah's conversation is interrupted by Sarah's parents, who call after seeing a picture of the promise ring on her Facebook page. In her bedroom, Sarah downplays the significance of the gift and her feelings for Evan, assuring them that her schoolwork and philanthropy are her main priorities. Her casual reassurance conceals her conflicting emotions about Evan and the future of their relationship.<!$Scr_Ps::3>}
