\par\pard\plain \tx0\li346\fi14\sb60\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 Sarah:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2> Sarah was concerned and anxious about what the promise ring from Evan meant. Her anxiety and feeling of guilt increased when her parents called about the promise ring based on Facebook, and Sarah downplayed her feelings for Evan and the significance of the promise ring. <!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 Katie:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2> Katie was being a supportive and compassionate friend for Sarah. However, Katie wasn't sure how to guide Sarah due to Sarah's indecision about a future with Evan.<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 Sarah's parents:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2> Sarah's parents, in particulate her father, were quite concerned when they saw Sarah had posted a a picture on Facebook of the promise ring Evan had given her. They were worried she was not sticking to her master plan.<!$Scr_Cs::2><!$Scr_Ps::4>}
